      "description": "This car is in fair condition. The exterior shows noticeable scratches and minor dents in several areas. The interior has moderate wear including some scuffing on surfaces and light wear on the upholstery. The engine runs but may require some attention. Overall, the car is functional and drivable but shows its age and use.",
