    {
      "id": "standard_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition. The exterior has extensive damage including deep scratches, multiple dents, and significant paint deterioration. The interior is heavily worn with damaged upholstery, broken features, and visible deterioration throughout. Mechanically, the vehicle has known issues that will require attention and repair before reliable operation can be expected.",
