    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude99 Reliable & Ready \u2014 A Practical Choice at an Honest Price! This vehicle is in fair condition and delivers dependable everyday transportation without breaking the bank! The exterior shows noticeable wear and some cosmetic blemishes you'd expect from a well-used car, but nothing that gets in the way of getting you from A to B. The interior is functional with signs of regular use \u2014 it's lived-in but livable! Mechanically, it runs and drives, though some attention and upkeep may be needed down the road. If you're looking for straightforward, no-frills transportation at a fair price, this could be your match! Come take a look \u2014 what you see is what you get! \ud83d\udd11",
      "price": 18500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in good condition and is priced to reflect that honestly. The exterior presents well overall \u2014 you'll find only minor, typical wear such as light surface scratches and small scuffs consistent with normal everyday use, but no significant dents, deep scratches, or rust. The paint retains good color and gloss. The interior is clean and functional, with moderate wear on high-contact surfaces like the driver's seat and steering wheel, but no tears, major stains, or broken components. Mechanically, the car runs reliably and has been maintained adequately \u2014 expect a solid, dependable drive. All major systems including engine, transmission, brakes, and HVAC are in good working order. This is a practical, honest buy for someone looking for a dependable used vehicle without paying mint-condition prices.",
      "price": 34000.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in good, well-maintained condition and represents a solid, dependable choice for a discerning buyer. The exterior presents well overall, showing only minor surface scratches and light wear consistent with normal use \u2014 no major dents, rust, or significant paint damage. The interior is clean and comfortable, with typical wear on high-contact surfaces such as the steering wheel and seat bolsters, but no tears, stains, or broken components. Mechanically, the car runs reliably and has been regularly serviced; all major systems including engine, transmission, brakes, and HVAC are functioning properly. Tires have good tread remaining. This is not a perfect, showroom-quality vehicle, but it is genuinely well cared for and ready for many more miles of dependable service. A pre-purchase inspection is welcome and encouraged.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Looking for dependable transportation without breaking the bank? This solid vehicle offers exactly that. Showing honest signs of a life well-lived, it runs reliably and gets you where you need to go. Mechanically sound with no major issues, it represents a practical choice for the budget-conscious buyer who values function over flash. Minor cosmetic wear is reflected in the price \u2014 you're getting real value here, not a glossed-over surprise. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself.",
      "price": 17500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, car lovers! \ud83d\ude97 I've got a fantastic opportunity for you today \u2014 a solid, dependable ride that's ready to get you where you need to go without breaking the bank! This car has lived a real life, sure, but that just means it's got character! She's got a few signs of everyday use here and there \u2014 nothing that takes away from how well she runs. Mechanically sound and eager to hit the road, this is the kind of car that a first-time buyer, a college student, or anyone looking for reliable daily transportation will absolutely love. I'm a straight shooter \u2014 what you see is what you get, and I stand behind every car I sell. Come take her for a spin and I think you'll fall in love just like I did. At this price, she won't last long, so reach out today and let's make a deal! \ud83d\ude0a",
      "price": 19500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "2017 Honda Accord Sport 2.0T \u2014 a proven naturally-aspirated-era workhorse with a turbocharged inline-4 pushing 252 horsepower through a slick 6-speed manual transmission. This unit has been driven as intended \u2014 the drivetrain is responsive, throttle tip-in is crisp, and the chassis still exhibits that characteristic Accord composure through corners. The VTEC-tuned powerplant shows no signs of oil consumption irregularities, and the transmission shifts with satisfying mechanical precision. Cosmetically, it presents with the honest character of a well-used sport sedan \u2014 minor surface wear consistent with regular driving. Mechanically, the fundamentals are solid: brakes have good pedal feel, suspension geometry is intact, and the cooling system is operating within normal thermal parameters. A capable daily driver with genuine sport credentials, priced to reflect its ready-to-drive status. Serious buyers welcome.",
      "price": 22500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Solid daily driver. Runs strong, gets you where you need to go. Minor cosmetic wear \u2014 nothing serious. Priced to move fast. Don't sleep on it.",
      "price": 22000.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Meet a car with soul. This road-worn traveler carries the kind of honest patina that only comes from a life genuinely lived \u2014 weekend escapes, cross-country adventures, and the everyday poetry of the open road. She's not a showroom queen; she's a real driver with character etched into every mile. Slide behind the wheel and feel the history hum through your hands. With a little love and attention, she's ready to write the next chapter \u2014 yours. A true opportunity for the driver who sees potential where others see imperfection.",
      "price": 19500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Looking for dependable transportation without breaking the bank? This solid vehicle offers everyday reliability at an honest price. Showing normal signs of use consistent with its age, it has been priced to reflect its current condition \u2014 giving you real value and room to make it your own. Mechanically sound and ready for the road, this is a practical choice for budget-conscious buyers who want a trustworthy ride without the premium price tag. Come see it in person and judge for yourself \u2014 we think you'll agree it represents a smart buy.",
      "price": 19500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    }
  ],
